name: O-Well
description:
A difficult platformer about building up the skill to overcome an obstacle.

Controls :

Arrow keys to move

Spacebar to jump

Hold Spacebar to jump higher

My personal best is 1 minute and 38.23 seconds.

Good luck.

Post your time in the comments if you want. No matter the time, if you get to the end you should be very proud of yourself.

This was done at Lojam 2019 and we had from January 11th to 13th.

Thanks to everyone who played it at the jam, and everyone who set the event up.

Credits:

Music was by Daniel Sottile

and I did the rest.
